title: The Troupe of Ten feat. Malia Baker, Kelly Jenrette & Kenny Leu
dc:creator: WBUR
description: Malia Baker (The Baby-Sitters Club, Are You Afraid of the Dark), Kelly Jenrette (The Handmaid's Tale, All-American: Homecoming) and Kenny Leu (A Shot Through the Wall, Midway) headline a story about a troupe of actors who always bring down the house, until they're nearly brought down themselves.
